\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Once upon a time, in a small village nestled between rolling hills and a sparkling river, lived a kind-hearted baker named Lars. His bakery was the heart of the village, not just for the delicious bread he baked, but for the warmth and kindness he extended to everyone.
\f1\fs24 \
