\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 \strokec2 One winter, the village was hit by a severe snowstorm. The river froze, the roads were blocked, and the villagers were trapped in their homes. Amidst this, Lars had a thought. He put on his warmest coat, packed a bag with loaves of bread, and stepped out into the snow.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
