\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf0 \strokec2 With great difficulty, he made his way from house to house, delivering bread to each family. The villagers were surprised and deeply touched by his gesture. His selfless act not only fed them but also brought them hope and comfort in those cold, dark days.
\f1\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 \
